## Project Context

This repository contains SaltStack configurations for Qubes OS template management.
The majority of content comes from the Qubes team as a framework, with custom modifications
primarily located under `/srv/salt/rynkowski/`.

## File Structure & Conventions

### Directory Structure
- `scripts/` - Management and automation scripts
- `dom0/srv/salt/` - SaltStack states and configurations
- `dom0/srv/salt/rynkowski/` - **Primary development area** - custom Salt states and modules
- Templates and states should be organized in logical subdirectories
